metadata.name: Libidinous No 3
metadata.description:
Series: 1 of 1  
Model: Astarte (https://www.instagram.com/astarte.anaisa/)  
Photographer: Marten Rauschenberg

"Fun fact: when shooting with a butt plug, it's not always controllable which direction the tail is orientated. During the main purpose of this sex toy, I guess it doesn't matter, but for our visual purposes, it was important that the tail was always "looking up". Gravitation and saliva however, made the tail swinging down every couple of seconds and Astarte had a hard time keeping it in position. Also, I added quite a couple of meters to my fitbit by running back and fourth between camera and tail-dressing. ;-)"
